{"meta":{"authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:24 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:24 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">The present tense is formed by placing after the verb the particles: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་རེད་</span> (assertive), <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་ </span>(testimonial), and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་</span> (egophoric). These are formed by adding an existential copula to the suffix<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> གི་</span>. The resulting auxiliaries have the same evidential value as the existential copulas. In modern conversational usage, the form <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་</span> is often abbreviated to <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གིས་</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">In English, these forms may be translated either by the progressive or the simple present depending on the context.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The various forms are presented in the following table:</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><strong>Table: The Present Tense Auxiliaries</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"97\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Affirmative</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(without pronoun)</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"149\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(with pronouns)</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"105\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"144\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative Interrogative</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"97\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"149\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"105\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"144\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མེད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"97\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་</span> / <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གིས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་གས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"149\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"105\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མི་འདུག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"144\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མི་འདུག་གས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"97\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"152\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"149\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"105\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་མ་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"144\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་མ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Some basic example sentences:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ང་ཁ་ལག་བཟོ་གི་ཡོད།</span> &ldquo;I am preparing the meal.&rdquo; (or) &ldquo;I prepare the meal.&rdquo; (egophoric)</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ང་ཡི་གེ་འབྲི་གི་ཡོད།</span> &ldquo;I am writing a letter.&rdquo; (or) &ldquo;I write letters.&rdquo; (egophoric)</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བློ་བཟང་ཁ་ལག་བཟོ་གི་ཡོད་རེད།</span> &ldquo;Lopzang prepares food.&rdquo; (or) &ldquo;Lopzang is preparing food.&rdquo; (assertive)</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བློ་བཟང་ཁ་ལག་བཟོ་གི་</span>(<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འདུག</span>) &ldquo;Lopzang is preparing food.&rdquo; (or) &ldquo;Lopzang prepares food.&rdquo; (testimonial)</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྡོ་རྗེ་ཡི་གེ་འབྲི་གི་ཡོད་རེད། </span>&ldquo;Dorj&eacute; writes letters.&rdquo; (or) &ldquo;Dorj&eacute; is writing a letter.&rdquo; (assertive)</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྡོ་རྗེ་ཡི་གེ་འབྲི་གི་</span>(<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འདུག</span>) &ldquo;Dorj&eacute; is writing a letter.&rdquo; (or) &ldquo;Dorj&eacute; writes letters.&rdquo; (testimonial)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Affirmative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(without pronoun)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Interrogative</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">(with pronouns)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Negative Interrogative</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མེད་པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་</span> / <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གིས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་གས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་འདུག་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མི་འདུག་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་མི་འདུག་གས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་མ་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གི་ཡོད་མ་རེད་པས་</span></p>\n","title":""}]}